{"tid":1696633,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"等我解釋比大家聽 何妖何君堯被刺既疑點","createTime":"2019-11-06T09:32:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-06T18:10:23.000Z","uid":133341,"like":8,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"c0060e2b0d7e5d34ef43c2ba8c48d6c4d0c460bf","tid":1696633,"uid":133341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T09:32:33.000Z","msg":"1. 點解會咁岩影到??<br />\n2. 未行埋去已經roll 定機??<br />\n3. 載同色同款帽??<br />\n4. 都係著藍色衫??<br />\n<br />\n如果有細心聽段片<br />\n有個阿嬸有講<strong><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">&quot;佢尋日都有黎&quot;</span></span></strong><br />\n所以烈士係有踩過線<br />\n前一日已經去探定路<br />\n做左好多準備<br />\n而我相信烈士係考慮過好多<br />\n計劃過好多先行動<br />\n<br />\n佢係<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">放棄自己既將來</span></span></strong><br />\n黎除去香港警黑亂局既一大重要人物<br />\n<br />\n依家佢係狗屋比黑警點<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">虐待</span></strong></span><br />\n點<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>侮辱</strong></span></span>都未有人理<br />\n<br />\n你地就個個割左佢<br />\n放棄佢<br />\n<br />\n如果我係鬼帶風向就死老豆死老母<br />\n我只係想大家唔好忘記<br />\n烈士同以往每一個義士都係一樣<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">大家係手足啊</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n請唔好忘記佢<br />\n一定要繼續關注佢<br />\n否則黑警又殺多個<br />\n重要比人話鬼<br />\n佢會死左都唔安落<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>另外<br />\n請大家都要關注周同學<br />\n無論黑警謀殺定誤殺<br />\n都要查到水落石出</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>光復香港<br />\n時代革命</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"43723062da60f74ebbaf0f7d4b144ba7eaa39950","tid":1696633,"uid":19178,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T09:33:41.000Z","msg":"weibo 同知乎上曬熱門就知咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29e3bb3622b18040e9287956f93a8b67c494fc7b","tid":1696633,"uid":133341,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-0